snippet.title: Dunki Drop 1 | Shah Rukh Khan | Rajkumar Hirani | Taapsee | Vicky | Boman | Christmas 2023
snippet.description:
Get ready to embark on this emotional rollercoaster of the most amazing journey ever taken, as we present to you the Dunki Drop 1.

Starring Shah Rukh Khan, Taapsee Pannu, Boman Irani and Vicky Kaushal, Dunki, directed by Rajkumar Hirani, and presented by Jio Studios, Red Chillies Entertainment and Rajkumar Hirani Films.

snippet.title: कौन है Bhide की ये हालत का जिम्मेदार? |  Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 4 Nov 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Tapu Sena plans to play night cricket. Bapuji has told Tapu not to trouble anyone. Tapu is angry at Goli's brother. Goli's brother has come to play cricket with them.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 0175
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Sivaangi & Harshavardhan La La Heartu Nikkala| Samodu Vilayadu 3 #samvishal #sivaangi #harshavardhan
snippet.description:
Beverage Partner: Dailee

#sivaangi #harshavardhan  #samoduvilayadu #samvishal #fun #games #gameshow  
Welcome to episode  of Samodu Vilayadu - Season 3, featuring Sivaangi & Harshavardhan ! In this hilarious episode, Sivaangi & Harsha showcase their incredible skills and entertain us with their energetic performance. Join us as we delve into the world of comedy and fun in this captivating episode of Samodu Vilayadu.

Episode 1: Chef Venkatesh Bhat and Cook with Comali Director Parthiv Mani: https://youtu.be/mTWVcAOg21M 

Episode 2: Binni mam & Kuraishi :https://youtu.be/CV2wOJfzWig

Episode 3: Vj Siddhu & Harshath khan:https://youtu.be/WZpCpM1OZxc

Episode 4 : Priya Jerson & Kaluthu karthi: https://youtu.be/t8T55Pu33Ko

Episode 5 : Roshini & Darshan :https://youtu.be/fI_RBGXJGDs

Episode 6 : Rj Sindhu & Arjun Manohar : https://youtu.be/iIUe2Lg5s2A

Episode 7 : Bharath & Anu : https://youtu.be/FlkAfIoDgLU

Episode 8 : Sivaangi & Harsha :https://youtu.be/oypz5vaU8l0

"Samodu Vilayadu" - the most entertaining and hilarious game show on the block! Hosted by the charismatic Sam Vishal and produced by the creative geniuses at Media Masons, this show is your ticket to fun, laughter, and the chance to take home over a lakh rupees in cash prizes!

In "Samodu Vilayadu," contestants from all walks of life team up as duos to compete in three exciting rounds of games and challenges that will put their wit, skills, and teamwork to the test. But that's not all – this game show is also a comedy extravaganza with an abundance of humor that will have you rolling with laughter!

If you're looking for a game show that combines fun, laughter, and the opportunity to win big, "Samodu Vilayadu" is the perfect choice. Join us for an unforgettable experience that will leave you entertained and energized!

Don't miss out on the fun – subscribe now, hit the notification bell, and tune in to "Samodu Vilayadu" for a rollercoaster of laughs and incredible cash prizes. Let the games begin! 🤣💰🎉

Today’s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 1 cup Milk
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1 cup Ghee
• 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
• Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
• When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
• Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you don’t use thick ghee. 
• Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
• Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
• Knead the mixture into dough. 
• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

#chakalirecipe #madhurasrecipe #bhajnichakli

Ingredients:
Bhajani
• 2 1/2 cup / 500 gm Rice
• 1 cup / 200 gm Chana dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Moong dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Urad dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Poha
• 20 gm Coriander seeds
• 20 gm Cumin seeds
Chakali
• 3 cups Water
• 1/4 cup Oil
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Coriander powder
• 1 kilo Chakali bhajani
• 1 tsp Ajwain / Carom seeds
• 1 tsp white Sesame seeds
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Wipe the rice really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe chana dal really good with clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe moong dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe urad dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• You can wash and dry all these ingredients if you want. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and roast rice really good. 
• The rice should be roasted well but the color should not change. 
• When the rice is roasted well take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast chana dal really good until it begins to get reddish color and take it out into 
  a dish. 
• In the same pan roast moong dal well until it gets reddish color and take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast urad dal really good until it gets light golden color and take it out into a 
  dish. 
• Roast poha really good and transfer them into the dish. 
• In the same pan roast coriander seeds and cumin seeds together on low heat until nice aroma 
  begins to release from it and transfer it into the dish. 
• Mix everything well together and let it cool down. 
• Grind it from the mill. Make sure that it is ground after rice or jawar is ground and not after wheat. 
• Blend it into flour in mixer and sieve it through flour strainer. 
• Blend the leftover coarse flour in the strain again in blender and sieve it. Bhajani for chakali is 
  ready.
Chakali
• Heat up water in a pan and add oil. 
• Mix well and add red chili powder, salt, coriander powder. 
• Mix well and when the mixture boils really good, reduce the heat to low. 
• Add the bhajani flour and turn off the gas. 
• Add carom seeds, sesame seeds and mix everything well together quickly. 
• Transfer the ukad into a dish and knead dough. If needed use very little hot water. 
• Knead the ukad really good when it is still hot. The consistency of the dough should be stiff. 
• Take small portion from the dough and knead it really good again. 
• Make a smooth and even roll and transfer it into chakali machine. 
• Press the dough well and roll out chakali from it on a butter paper. 
• Seal both the ends of the chakali really good. 
•You can use plastic sheet or dish in place of butter paper. 
• Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
• If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
• Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
• When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
• When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
• Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready.

snippet.title: Unlocking the Secrets of the Malik Family | LOL PODCAST |
snippet.description:
"LOL Podcast के इस खास एपिसोड में, हम जानेंगे अरमान मलिक, कृतिका मलिक, और पायल मलिक की अद्वितीय प्रेम कहानी के बारे में। अरमान ने कृतिका और पायल के साथ शादी की है, और वे सबकुछ साझा करके खुश और सफल जीवन बिता रहे हैं। हम साथ चलें और जानें उनके असामान्य रिश्ते, उन्होंने कैसे समस्याओं का सामना किया, और उनके पॉपुलर YouTube चैनल्स के पीछे के राज। समझें कैसे उन्होंने समाजिक नियमों को तोड़कर प्यार और खुशी पाई, और सफल सामग्री निर्माणकर्ता के रूप में उनके प्रेरणास्पद सफर के बारे में। इस दिलचस्प एपिसोड को ना देखने पर, प्यार की सभी रूपों की प्रशंसा करने वाला मौका न गवाएं।"

In this special episode of Bharti TV we delve into the extraordinary love story of Arman Malik, Kritika Malik, and Payal Malik,  Arman is married to both Kritika and Payal, and they're living a happy and successful life together. Join us as we explore their unconventional relationship, the challenges they've faced, and the secrets behind their thriving YouTube channels. Discover how they've defied societal norms to find love and happiness, and learn about their inspiring journey as successful content creators. Don't miss this fascinating episode that celebrates love in all its forms. 

bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya #armaanmalik #payalmalik #kritikamalik #chirayumalik #vlog

(00:00) - Precap

(31:58) - Are people jealous of malik family 
(33:21) - Thought's on Bigg Boss !
(37:07) - Payal ke thoughts on family
(38:02) - End note 
(40:17) - Special segment with chirayu malik

snippet.title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Director Wes Ball breathes new life into the global, epic franchise set several generations in the future following Caesar’s reign, in which apes are the dominant species living harmoniously and humans have been reduced to living in the shadows. As a new tyrannical ape leader builds his empire, one young ape undertakes a harrowing journey that will cause him to question all that he has known about the past and to make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.

“Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes” is directed by Wes Ball (the “Maze Runner” trilogy) and stars Owen Teague (“IT”), Freya Allan (“The Witcher”), Kevin Durand (Locke & Key”), Peter Macon (“Shameless”), and William H. Macy (“Fargo”). The screenplay is by Josh Friedman (“War of the Worlds”) and Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver (“Avatar: The Way of Water”) and Patrick Aison (“Prey”), based on characters created by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and the producers are Wes Ball, Joe Hartwick, Jr. (“The Maze Runner”), Rick Jaffa, Amanda Silver, Jason Reed (“Mulan”), with Peter Chernin (the “Planet of the Apes” trilogy) and Jenno Topping (“Ford v. Ferrari”) serving as executive producers.

snippet.title: NOVEMBER 3 (Official Video) | Akaal | Latest Punjabi Songs 2023
snippet.description:
Presenting the video of our new punjabi song November 3 by Akaal in which music is given by Jassi X while the lyrics of this latest punjabi song are penned by Jashan Jagdev.
#punjabisong #latestpunjabisongs #newpunjabisongs 

Song: November 3
Singer: Akaal
Music: Jassi X
Lyrics: Jashan Jagdev
Director - Sukh D
Female Lead - Geet Goraya
Music Label: T-Series

Lyrics -

Teri meri meri teri mulaqat June di,
Ve pehli pehli raat neend ayi na skoon ਦੀ,
Jashan jagdev tu hi jcheya jatti nu, gede mere piche londe c lfandr bde,
Aunde saal ik paasa Kr ve jatta, tu  tere laareya ch lng gye November bde,

college di tenu prdhaangi to wehl na, 
ve menu eh fikr, kite ho jaawein tu fail na, 
Jehde tere beli tenu chukna jyi dinde aa, ve ohna di njaij metho ban jaawe rail na, 
Oda coffee shop te lijaanda ni kde tu, kath yaaran naal krda ptaNder bde, 
Aunde saal ik paasa Kr ve jatta, tu  tere laareya ch lng gye November bde,

Jagdev kalan walea tu Akdaan wikhona aen, 
Ve sohal mutyar jaan jaan k stauna aen, 
kdraan ni Tenu, menu khbraan ne saariyan, Ve kihde gaane likhda, te kihde lyi tu gauna aen, 
21iyaan to Hogi 25 saal di jatta ਮੈਂ, bdle udeeka ch callender bde, 
Aunde saal ik paasa Kr ve jatta, tu  tere laareya ch lng gye November bde,

puch lyi akaal ਤੋਂ ਲਿਖਾਇਆ shream mai
tattoo khunwa lea veeni te tera nam mai, 
dil maajhe aale jatta har gyi tnu mai, oda firde c jitde sikander bde,
aunde saal ik paasa Kr ve jatta, tu  tere laareya ch lng gye November bde

snippet.title: Milk Sweet recipe in Tamil | Kalakand Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make milk sweet recipe in tamil. This milk sweet / Kalakand is made by curdling milk with some lemon juice which creates some precipitated milk curds and these are then caramelized under heat to impart that rich, chewy, caramel taste. Compared to the regular milk sweet, this version has a lot more texture and chewiness to it. This Kalakand recipe is popular during festival time and can be topped with some nuts.
#milksweetrecipe #milksweetrecipeintamil #kalakandrecipe 

Friends, please do try this milk sweet recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking! 

Ingredients:
2 Liter full fat Milk (8 cup)
1 cup Sugar(200g) can be increased to 1.25 cup
juice of half Lemon
2+2 tbsp Ghee
pinch of Cardamom powder

Oh manikuruvi

Malvaatheril

Nnavan enne

Enn maayavaani

snippet.title: Daya ने क्यों मारा Jetha के पेट पे मुक्का? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Revisit The Journey
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Bhide has come to Jetha's house to complain about Tapu's carelessness in his studies. Jetha challenges Bhide on the same and informs him that Tapu is busy studying. They all find out that Tapu was reading comics all this while and Jetha gets angry at him. Later, Tapu's class teacher tells everyone that they will be having a parent-teacher meeting which is mandatory for all to attend.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 343
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

About me:

The smallest countryside, a beautiful childhood was my past. It is a glorious experience but remains like the memory of a past life.
Due to an endless wish, persistent effort, and a grateful companionship with my better half, I was able to create my little Brindavan in the outskirts of Hyderabad just as I dreamed.
We do not know if it was our mindset, but we managed to create Patnam lo Palleturu- Our little long lost village in the city. 
We believe in living life and not in just Surviving.

I have come forward to have fun with you in a world of small and beautiful dreams.
This includes our home, beautiful garden, our Grandparents' food recipes, health tips, modern steps and the desire to share my thoughts with you.

అతి చిన్న పల్లెటూరు, అందమైన బాల్యం నా గతం. అది ఎంతో అపురూపమైనది కానీ గత జన్మలా మిగిలిపోయింది.
అంతులేని కోరిక, భగీరథ ప్రయత్నం, తోడుగా నా జీవిత భాగస్వామి, వెరసి నేను కలలుగన్న బృందావనం కుటీరం హైదరాబాద్ నగరం చేరువలో.

మనసు పడ్డామా, మార్పుని కోరుకుంటున్నామా, ఏమో తెలియదు కానీ, మొత్తానికి పట్నంలో పల్లెను సృష్టించుకున్నాం. బ్రతికే యడం కాదు జీవిద్దాం అనే మా కోరికకు జీవం పోసుకున్నాం.

ఆర్భాటాలు లేని, అందమైన కలల ప్రపంచం లో మీతో కలసి ఆనందించాలని మీ ముందుకు వచ్చాను.
ఇందులో మా కుటీరం, అందమైన వనం, అమ్మమ్మ వంటలు ,ఆరోగ్య సూత్రాలు, ఆధునిక అడుగుల తో పాటు నా ఆలోచన స్రవంతిని మీతో పంచుకోవాలనే కోరికకు రూపమే ఈ కలగూరగంప.

ఇట్లు

Episode 3919: NASA Se Call
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka and Bagha are ecstatic about their great sale over the holiday season. They relay the news to Jetha as he walks into the business, but he appears to be lost in his thoughts. Bagha tells about his meeting with a donkey. Bagha informs his boss that a kicking donkey is regarded as extremely fortunate, but Jetha is skeptical. Jetha later receives a call from NASA. Watch the show to find out why an American space station contacted Jetha.

snippet.title: The Beatles - Now And Then (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Now and Then's eventful journey to fruition took place over five decades and is the product of conversations and collaborations between the four Beatles that go on to this day. The long mythologised John Lennon demo was first worked on in February 1995 by Paul, George and Ringo as part of The Beatles Anthology project but it remained unfinished, partly because of the impossible technological challenges involved in working with the vocal John had recorded on tape in the 1970s. For years it looked like the song could never be completed. But in 2022 there was a stroke of serendipity. A software system developed by Peter Jackson and his team, used throughout the production of the documentary series Get Back, finally opened the way for the uncoupling of John’s vocal from his piano part. As a result, the original recording could be brought to life and worked on anew with contributions from all four Beatles. This remarkable story of musical archaeology reflects The Beatles’ endless creative curiosity and shared fascination with technology. It marks the completion of the last recording that John, Paul and George and Ringo will get to make together and celebrates the legacy of the foremost and most influential band in popular music history.

Video Director: Peter Jackson
Video Producers: Peter Jackson, Clare Olssen, Jonathan Clyde
Audio Producers: Paul McCartney and Giles Martin
Production Company: WingNut Films Productions Ltd

Elvish Yadav | बिग बॉस ओटीटी विनर एल्विश यादव (Elvish Yadav) सांपों की तस्करी और गैरकानूनी रेव पार्टी करवाने के मामले में बुरे फंसे हैं. इस मामले में 5 आरोपियों को गिरफ्तार कर लिया गया है. वहीं, एल्विश यादव के फरार होने की खबरें हैं. इस बीच एल्विश यादव का बयान आया. उन्होंने पुलिस की कार्रवाई में सहयोग करने की बात कही है. मामले को लेकर नोएडा डीसीपी की प्रतिक्रिया आयी है.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: The Fall Guy | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Stuntman becomes the hero. #TheFallGuyMovie only in theaters March 1.

------

He’s a stuntman, and like everyone in the stunt community, he gets blown up, shot, crashed, thrown through windows and dropped from the highest of heights, all for our entertainment. And now, fresh off an almost career-ending accident, this working-class hero has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job. What could possibly go right? 

From real life stunt man and director David Leitch, the blockbuster director of Bullet Train, Deadpool 2, Atomic Blonde and Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and the producer of John Wick, Nobody and Violent Night, comes his most personal film yet. A new hilarious, hard-driving, all-star apex-action thriller and love letter to action movies and the hard-working and under-appreciated crew of people who make them: The Fall Guy. 

Oscar® nominee Ryan Gosling (Barbie, La La Land, Drive) stars as Colt Seavers, a battle-scarred stuntman who, having left the business a year earlier to focus on both his physical and mental health, is drafted back into service when the star of a mega-budget studio movie—being directed by his ex, Jody Moreno, played by Golden Globe winner Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place films, Sicario)—goes missing.

While the film’s ruthless producer (Emmy winner Hannah Waddingham; Ted Lasso), maneuvers to keep the disappearance of star Tom Ryder (Golden Globe winner Aaron Taylor-Johnson; Bullet Train) a secret from the studio and the media, Colt performs the film’s most outrageous stunts while trying (with limited success) to charm his way back into Jody’s good graces. But as the mystery around the missing star deepens, Colt will find himself ensnared in a sinister, criminal plot that will push him to the edge of a fall more dangerous than any stunt.

Inspired by the hit 1980s TV series, The Fall Guy also stars Winston Duke (Black Panther franchise) and Academy Award® nominee Stephanie Hsu (Everything Everywhere All at Once). 

From a screenplay by Hobbs & Shaw screenwriter Drew Pearce, The Fall Guy is produced by Kelly McCormick (Bullet Train, Nobody, Atomic Blonde) and David Leitch for their company 87North, and by Ryan Gosling and by Guymon Casady (Game of Thrones, Steve Jobs and executive producer of the upcoming series Ripley) for Entertainment 360. The film is executive produced by Drew Pearce, Entertainment 360’s Geoff Shaevitz and the creator of the original Fall Guy television series, Glen A. Larson.

Jetha and Tapu's friends wait for Tapus's call from Paris. Everyone is worried. Meanwhile, Tapu and Champaklal parade around Paris and represent India in the competition.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi
Episode - 1198
#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch the 'Comedy Lagataar' episodes from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZAg6W-3De1ssi64wfuZyw6

snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, envisioning #Vijay in the LCU, and more 

This is the first part of the interaction.   #CinemaExpress 

00:10 - 01:45  - Loki and The Kerala Story
01:46 - 02:45 - How did Loki respond to the polarising responses 
02:46 - 04:40 - How did Loki accept the criticism about the flashback
04:41 - 08.40 - How Loki fixed the duration of Leo
08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo? 
24:39 - 25:43 - Loki opens about the Hulk Connect in Leo
25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo? 
32:31 - 32:56 - What is Parthiban's take on a drug-free society? 
32:57 - 33.24 - Does Loki really think the twin angle worked in favour of the film? 
33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room? 
37:59 - 42:05 - Does Loki feel the pressure of casting the big names
42:06 - 50:00 - The big question of Loki and LCU

Join the Nakkalites Fzone team as they explore the challenges and joys of baby planning in a rural village. From traditional rituals to modern parenting techniques, this heartwarming video showcases the unique experiences and support systems that exist in rural communities. snippet.title: Battle Like Champions' Champion! (Clash of Clans Season Challenges)
snippet.description:
The Champions' Champion skin joins the pantheon of Heroes as we celebrate this year's World Championship, live on Nov 24-26! Get your tickets now at https://supr.cl/clashfest2023! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Episode 3918: Chand Par Zameen
--------------------------------------------------------
Sundar pays Jetha a surprise visit and assures her that Daya may return by Diwali. Jetha is ecstatic by the news. Sundar and his buddies then advise Jetha about a particular tract of land that can be purchased for a very low price. Jetha becomes inquisitive and inquires of Sundar about its whereabouts. Jetha is informed by Sundar that the plot is accessible on the Moon. Jetha is taken aback at first, but he gradually begins to trust Sundar's remarks. Sundar informs Jetha that he purchased an area and wishes for Jetha to do the same. Is Jetha interested in this lunar plot?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3918, 2 Nov 2023

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Vijay | ENG Subs
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

*English subtitles have been added to the video to reach a wider audience.*

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171

snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
सरिताज किचनचे प्रॉडक्ट्स | Saritas Kitchen Products -
 1. सर्व प्रकारची लाकडी घाणा तेलं | All Types of Wood Pressed Oils
 2. डंकावर कुटून केलेला कांदा लसूण मसाला | Handmade Kanda Lasun Masala
 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt
 5. सेंद्रियहळद | Organic Turmeric
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - http://bitly.ws/zDuc

1/2 kg बेसनाचे लाडू दाणेदार, न बसणारे होण्यासाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | असे ओळखा तुपाचे प्रमाण Besan Ladu

बेसन लाडू 
बेसन लाडू रेसिपी | दिवाळी सणानिमित्त खास लाडू रेसिपी | सोपे व झटपट होणारे बेसन लाडू | दिवाळी फराळ रेसिपी | दिवाळी स्पेशल लाडू रेसिपी | लाडू व  बेसन भाजण्याची योग्य पद्धत | जिभेवर विरघळतील अशे खुसखुशीत बेसन लाडू |  Besan Ladu Recipe | Crispy Besan Ladu Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Easy and Quick Besan Ladu | Diwali Faral Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Besan Ladu Perfect Recipe | Mouth Melting Crispy Besan Ladu | 
साहित्य | Ingredients 
वजनी प्रमाण (या प्रमाणात केल्यावर तयार लाडू १ किलो होतात) 
 • हरभरा डाळ 500 ग्रॅम | Chana dal 500 gram
 • साजूक तूप 150-200 ग्रॅम | Ghee150-200 gram
 • पिठी साखर 400 ग्रॅम | Sugar Powder 400 gram
 • वेलची पूड   ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते  |  Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे  | Bedane 

वाटीचे प्रमाण | Cup Measurements
 • हरभरा डाळ 4 कप  | Chana dal 4 cups 
 • साजूक तूप पाउण कप आणि 2 मोठे चमचे  | Ghee 3/4 Cup + 2 tbsp
 • पिठी साखर 2 कप | Sugar Powder 2 cups 
 • वेलची पूड ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते | Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे | Bedane 
 • 
To make Besan Aata 

 • Saute chana dal for 10 to 12 minutes till it changes in light golden colour. 
 • After cooling grind all. 

Besan Ladu Recipe 

 • On low heat, Saute chana dal to the kadhai.  
 • After 2 to 3 minutes, add remaining ghee and saute for 20 to 22 minutes till its get light golden colour. 

 • After 20 minutes, sprinkle 2 tsp of water / milk, saute for 2 minutes and let them cool down. 
 • After cooling add sugar powder, cardamom powder, bedane and make all the ladu. 

Other Recipes 

1/2 किलो रव्याचे परफेक्ट खुसखुशीत पाकातले रवा लाडू| पाक चुकल्यास वापरा या 5 टिप्स Rava Ladoo Marathi
https://youtu.be/6HVj_CseLgQ?si=dT15QQ7XJ8xb2ICz

या 9 टिप्स वापरून बनवा गोल एकसारखी बूंदी आणि आतपर्यंत पाक मुरलेले खुसखुशीत बुंदीचे लाडू। bundi ladu
https://youtu.be/R1O7aYKchEQ?si=Mg3RUnDt5iTV_jcb

सर्वात सोप्या पद्धतीने या 5 टिप्स वापरून बनवा बिनापाकाचे रवा बेसन लाडू 1/2 किलो प्रमाणात Besan Ladoo
https://youtu.be/OFVQR0XmwcU?si=1qoL9kufLycb08u2

1/2 वाटी तुपात गव्हाच्या पिठाचे खुसखुशीत दाणेदार चुरमा लाडू | Churma Ladu Recipe Saritas Kitchen
https://youtu.be/Zd5NZedFPNs?si=XRT66kK03oKNrWK8

कोणतेही महाग सामान न वापरता जगातील सगळ्यात पौष्टिक खुसखुशीत लाडू, घरातील उपलब्ध सामानात। Poushtik La
https://youtu.be/az_lStcS5Ek?si=uTeuIaErs7FF6zf0

दिवाळीसाठी 1 कप बेसनाचे ½Kg मोतीचूर लाडू| मार्केटसारखा मोतीचूर बनवण्याची परफेक्ट रेसिपी MotichurLadu
https://youtu.be/RnexeXfdfsA?si=LdmMjmmKjteB1xAj

1/2 kg बेसनाचे लाडू दाणेदार, न बसणारे होण्यासाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | असे ओळखा तुपाचे प्रमाण Besan Ladu

बेसन लाडू 
बेसन लाडू रेसिपी | दिवाळी सणानिमित्त खास लाडू रेसिपी | सोपे व झटपट होणारे बेसन लाडू | दिवाळी फराळ रेसिपी | दिवाळी स्पेशल लाडू रेसिपी | लाडू व  बेसन भाजण्याची योग्य पद्धत | जिभेवर विरघळतील अशे खुसखुशीत बेसन लाडू |  Besan Ladu Recipe | Crispy Besan Ladu Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Easy and Quick Besan Ladu | Diwali Faral Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Besan Ladu Perfect Recipe | Mouth Melting Crispy Besan Ladu | 
साहित्य | Ingredients 
वजनी प्रमाण (या प्रमाणात केल्यावर तयार लाडू १ किलो होतात) 
 • हरभरा डाळ 500 ग्रॅम | Chana dal 500 gram
 • साजूक तूप 150-200 ग्रॅम | Ghee150-200 gram
 • पिठी साखर 400 ग्रॅम | Sugar Powder 400 gram
 • वेलची पूड   ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते  |  Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे  | Bedane 

वाटीचे प्रमाण | Cup Measurements
 • हरभरा डाळ 4 कप  | Chana dal 4 cups 
 • साजूक तूप पाउण कप आणि 2 मोठे चमचे  | Ghee 3/4 Cup + 2 tbsp
 • पिठी साखर 2 कप | Sugar Powder 2 cups 
 • वेलची पूड ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते | Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे | Bedane 
 • 
To make Besan Aata 

 • Saute chana dal for 10 to 12 minutes till it changes in light golden colour. 
 • After cooling grind all. 

Besan Ladu Recipe 

 • On low heat, Saute chana dal to the kadhai.  
 • After 2 to 3 minutes, add remaining ghee and saute for 20 to 22 minutes till its get light golden colour. 

 • After 20 minutes, sprinkle 2 tsp of water / milk, saute for 2 minutes and let them cool down. 
 • After cooling add sugar powder, cardamom powder, bedane and make all the ladu. 

Other Recipes
